{"talk":{"id":58979,"name":"Yifat Susskind: In uncertain times, think like a mother","description":"There's a simple and powerful way to confront the world's most pressing crises, says women's rights activist Yifat Susskind: think like a mother. As she puts it: \"When you think like a mother, you prioritize the needs of the many, not the whims of the few.\" Follow along as she shares moving stories of people around the world who embody this mindset -- and shows how it can also help you see beyond suffering and act to build a better world.","slug":"yifat_susskind_in_uncertain_times_think_like_a_mother","recorded_at":"2019-12-04 00:00:00","published_at":"2020-04-06 14:50:53","updated_at":"2022-02-23 15:57:54","viewed_count":0,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":618,"name":"TEDWomen 2019"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/b715964f7798627c274e313b881eeae28ce9f290_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/b715964f7798627c274e313b881eeae28ce9f290_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/b715964f7798627c274e313b881eeae28ce9f290_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/b715964f7798627c274e313b881eeae28ce9f290_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/9ee5c653f0b773f7f0da0fea27f7cfd59c9000a6_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/YifatSusskind_2019W-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":5164511,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/YifatSusskind_2019W-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":14287320,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/YifatSusskind_2019W-320k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":25314542,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"450k":{"uri":"